        </div>
        <h3 class="bento-title">Competitor gap mining</h3>
        <h4 class="bento-sub">The searches they rank for. <span class="accent">You don't.</span> Yet.</h4>
        <p class="bento-desc">Drop in 5 rival domains. theStacc pulls every keyword they sit in the top 20 for that your site doesn't touch. You see the list, sorted by traffic, in 30 seconds flat.</p>
