          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Tagged · informational · buying · local</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Difficulty score · pick the easy wins</li>
