          <div class="bento-social-row"><span class="bento-social-icon">PPX</span><span class="bento-social-text">"how long does invisalign take adults"</span><span class="bento-social-status">●</span></div>
          <div class="bento-social-row"><span class="bento-social-icon">GEM</span><span class="bento-social-text">"cheapest way to fix a clogged drain"</span><span class="bento-social-status">●</span></div>
